WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:15.840 --> 00:01:16.840
Let's make a deal.

00:01:17.599 --> 00:01:18.519
Hand him over to me.

00:01:18.719 --> 00:01:20.319
Name your price.

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:22.439
No deal.

00:01:25.599 --> 00:01:26.280
Fine.

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:28.599
Because the Liu Family failed to act in time,

00:01:28.760 --> 00:01:29.879
Houzi ended up dead.

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:32.079
I solemnly apologize for that.

00:01:33.519 --> 00:01:34.879
Why apologize to Houzi?

00:01:36.480 --> 00:01:37.400
Whether it's us

00:01:37.799 --> 00:01:38.599
or Houzi,

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:40.159
killing or being killed

00:01:40.599 --> 00:01:41.359
is to be expected.

00:01:42.280 --> 00:01:44.000
The Liu Family won't shield a criminal.

00:01:44.480 --> 00:01:45.200
So,

00:01:46.359 --> 00:01:47.439
for Houzi's death,

00:01:47.760 --> 00:01:49.040
I'm the one who should apologize.

00:01:53.879 --> 00:01:54.959
But Xiao Baojie,

00:01:55.319 --> 00:01:56.760
she's a kind-hearted child.

00:01:57.280 --> 00:01:59.280
She is who the Liu Family should protect.

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:04.120
Why did you only act

00:02:04.879 --> 00:02:06.280
after we stepped in?

00:02:12.879 --> 00:02:13.719
Cut the act.

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:16.360
Any later and we'll miss dinner.

00:02:18.759 --> 00:02:20.599
Look who's here, damn Limpy.

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:24.879
Should've come later

00:02:25.360 --> 00:02:27.039
and get your other good leg wrecked too.

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:28.680
Then you'd be in a wheelchair.

00:02:30.879 --> 00:02:34.240
The guy who ran off today,

00:02:34.719 --> 00:02:36.240
Wang Qiusheng, right?

00:02:38.599 --> 00:02:41.199
A spooked rabbit's first instinct

00:02:41.199 --> 00:02:42.879
is to run back to its den.

00:02:43.800 --> 00:02:44.520
Find him.

00:02:45.599 --> 00:02:46.240
Take him out.

00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:50.599
You came here on this thing?

00:02:51.719 --> 00:02:52.879
It was the fastest ride

00:02:52.879 --> 00:02:54.159
I could find nearby.

00:02:54.240 --> 00:02:54.840
How about it?

00:02:55.080 --> 00:02:55.840
Pretty cool, right?

00:02:56.479 --> 00:02:57.759
You can feel the breeze riding on it.

00:02:57.960 --> 00:02:59.400
Xiao Baojie will definitely love it.

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:01.800
I want to ride that one!

00:03:10.439 --> 00:03:11.639
This car is kinda stuffy.

00:03:15.319 --> 00:03:16.159
Hold onto this for me.

00:03:16.240 --> 00:03:16.840
It's all yours.

00:03:24.439 --> 00:03:25.400
There's more room out here.

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:27.479
Tongtong can rest and enjoy the breeze.

00:03:31.400 --> 00:03:32.280
Why aren't we moving?

00:03:32.879 --> 00:03:35.479
Why the hell should I be your chauffeur?

00:03:38.639 --> 00:03:39.759
Get out.

00:03:43.919 --> 00:03:46.039
On such a beautiful, sunny day,

00:03:46.039 --> 00:03:48.240
going on an outing with good friends

00:03:48.479 --> 00:03:50.520
is quite a pleasant experience.

00:03:50.639 --> 00:03:51.400
After all,

00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:52.560
we're as close as brothers,

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:53.560
one big happy family.

00:03:56.080 --> 00:03:57.240
You've lost your mind.

00:03:58.919 --> 00:03:59.840
I know

00:03:59.919 --> 00:04:01.360
you hold a grudge against me,

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:02.159
but I don't blame you.

00:04:02.360 --> 00:04:04.360
I'll win you over with love.

00:04:04.520 --> 00:04:06.159
You must be sick in the head again.

00:04:06.639 --> 00:04:07.800
Uncle Houzi.

00:04:08.360 --> 00:04:08.919
Tongtong.

00:04:08.919 --> 00:04:09.639
Tongtong's awake.

00:04:10.759 --> 00:04:12.120
They were all fighting just now.

00:04:12.919 --> 00:04:15.240
Limpy also hit their heads with his crutch.

00:04:16.959 --> 00:04:17.600
I...

00:04:18.199 --> 00:04:19.040
Madman hit them too.

00:04:19.319 --> 00:04:20.160
He used a stick.

00:04:22.079 --> 00:04:24.240
Simpleton's really getting the hang of it.

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:25.680
I'll kill him sooner or later.

00:04:25.759 --> 00:04:26.560
Shameless.

00:04:26.959 --> 00:04:27.720
Disgusting.

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:37.040
Where's Uncle Houzi?

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:40.879
Is he okay?

00:05:13.360 --> 00:05:14.160
Actually,

00:05:14.879 --> 00:05:16.480
we should've all been dead long ago.

00:05:17.240 --> 00:05:19.000
Every extra day we live is a blessing.

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:20.639
This was Houzi's fate.

00:05:20.680 --> 00:05:21.680
And it'll be ours someday.

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:22.879
It's got nothing to do with you.

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:30.759
But Uncle Houzi really died because of me.

00:05:31.439 --> 00:05:32.079
You're wrong.

00:05:33.399 --> 00:05:34.800
Whether it's Houzi or the rest of us,

00:05:35.600 --> 00:05:36.720
everything we've done

00:05:36.839 --> 00:05:37.879
isn't just for you.

00:05:38.680 --> 00:05:39.560
We're also

00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:41.600
trying to reclaim our own hearts.

00:05:42.199 --> 00:05:43.480
When folks from the Black Street do good,

00:05:43.720 --> 00:05:44.639
they always need an excuse.

00:05:44.839 --> 00:05:45.639
You just happen

00:05:45.839 --> 00:05:47.279
to be that excuse.

00:05:47.639 --> 00:05:48.519
Do people from the Black Street

00:05:48.720 --> 00:05:49.959
really love killing that much?

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:52.759
You did hit their heads with your crutch.

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:54.040
I can vouch for it.

00:05:54.199 --> 00:05:55.399
He's terrifying when he hits people.

00:05:55.759 --> 00:05:57.160
These two morons.

00:05:57.399 --> 00:05:58.279
Total morons.

00:05:58.560 --> 00:05:59.560
At least the two of us

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:02.319
can run freely in the sunshine.

00:06:04.759 --> 00:06:05.399
Limpy,

00:06:05.959 --> 00:06:07.120
I just remembered,

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:08.279
it seems

00:06:08.519 --> 00:06:09.959
you were running pretty fast just now.

00:06:13.199 --> 00:06:14.000
Maybe

00:06:14.199 --> 00:06:16.920
you can run freely in the sunshine too.

00:06:17.240 --> 00:06:17.839
How about it,

00:06:21.199 --> 00:06:21.879
Simpleton?

00:06:23.439 --> 00:06:24.399
Execute the plan.

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:25.519
What plan?

00:06:26.079 --> 00:06:28.240
Black Street top-secret plan, Article 15.

00:06:30.279 --> 00:06:31.360
The Running Limpy.

00:06:34.680 --> 00:06:35.639
Let me hold this for you.

00:06:36.279 --> 00:06:37.000
What the hell?

00:06:42.560 --> 00:06:43.199
Reporting in.

00:06:43.279 --> 00:06:44.079
Mission accomplished.

00:06:44.199 --> 00:06:44.879
Well done.

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:47.319
I hereby solemnly declare

00:06:47.720 --> 00:06:48.800
that you've saved the world.

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:50.519
A child's world.

00:06:54.199 --> 00:06:55.240
You two morons,

00:06:56.040 --> 00:06:56.959
when we get back to the Black Street,

00:06:57.079 --> 00:06:58.279
I'm gonna duel both of you.

00:07:01.920 --> 00:07:02.600
Tongtong.

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:03.399
He's so silly.

00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:33.759
Brother Su Yang and Uncle Limpy,

00:07:33.759 --> 00:07:35.519
they said a lot,

00:07:37.560 --> 00:07:39.959
but I still want to thank you.

00:07:40.560 --> 00:07:42.240
Thank you for trying to save me.

00:07:44.839 --> 00:07:47.240
I don't know why everyone says

00:07:47.759 --> 00:07:49.800
I'm a ray of light in their hearts.

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:52.399
But your ray of light

00:07:52.639 --> 00:07:55.000
will shine in my heart forever.

00:08:32.399 --> 00:08:33.200
Today,

00:08:34.279 --> 00:08:36.000
the night sky is still beautiful.

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:37.600
But

00:08:38.759 --> 00:08:40.639
Uncle Houzi is gone.

00:10:09.559 --> 00:10:10.320
Hello,

00:10:10.879 --> 00:10:12.279
my new test subject.

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:14.639
Let me introduce myself.

00:10:14.960 --> 00:10:16.000
My name is Su Yang.

00:10:16.519 --> 00:10:17.200
A doctor.

00:10:17.720 --> 00:10:18.480
My specialty?

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:21.320
Making people wish they were dead.

00:10:29.799 --> 00:10:31.679
Don't disturb her rest.

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:33.720
I...

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:36.879
I said,

00:10:37.399 --> 00:10:40.000
don't disturb her rest.

00:10:41.759 --> 00:10:42.559
Quiet,

00:10:43.840 --> 00:10:44.639
obedient,

00:10:45.120 --> 00:10:46.080
and well-behaved.

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:50.200
These are essentials for a test subject.

00:10:51.039 --> 00:10:51.879
Got it?

00:11:12.080 --> 00:11:13.720
Don't bleed on the floor.

00:11:14.279 --> 00:11:15.840
It's a pain to clean up.

00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:11.559
Welcome to my laboratory.

00:13:18.759 --> 00:13:21.399
You know how afraid I am,

00:13:22.200 --> 00:13:23.240
afraid that one day

00:13:23.799 --> 00:13:25.000
I'll forget these images.

00:13:31.879 --> 00:13:33.240
So I write them down,

00:13:33.679 --> 00:13:34.519
and look at them often.

00:13:35.480 --> 00:13:36.960
Even though every time I look at them,

00:13:38.399 --> 00:13:39.720
my head hurts terribly.

00:13:41.799 --> 00:13:42.720
But only this way

00:13:43.200 --> 00:13:44.919
can I remember him for a long time.

00:13:47.519 --> 00:13:48.200
Congratulations.

00:13:49.480 --> 00:13:51.120
You've seen my biggest secret.

00:13:59.080 --> 00:13:59.679
Here.

00:14:00.799 --> 00:14:01.360
Take your medicine.

00:14:02.080 --> 00:14:03.320
Otherwise, during the surgery,

00:14:03.759 --> 00:14:04.480
the scalpel might slip.

00:14:05.120 --> 00:14:05.720
Come on.

00:14:09.080 --> 00:14:09.960
Take it.

00:14:17.559 --> 00:14:19.759
Finally, an Immortal has arrived.

00:14:22.679 --> 00:14:24.519
What a delightful evening.

00:14:33.279 --> 00:14:34.039
Don't move.

00:14:34.320 --> 00:14:35.360
This drug is expensive.

00:14:36.559 --> 00:14:38.360
It keeps you fully conscious

00:14:38.759 --> 00:14:39.480
while at the same time

00:14:39.759 --> 00:14:40.960
stripping away your mobility.

00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:46.320
How's that?

00:14:46.799 --> 00:14:47.480
Impressive, right?

00:15:13.960 --> 00:15:15.639
480.

00:15:16.919 --> 00:15:18.759
460.

00:15:19.519 --> 00:15:21.159
469.

00:15:21.720 --> 00:15:23.159
I miscounted.

00:15:24.919 --> 00:15:26.200
Don't interrupt me.

00:15:28.039 --> 00:15:29.600
What number was I on?

00:15:31.600 --> 00:15:32.240
Forget it.

00:15:32.480 --> 00:15:33.200
Start over.

00:15:35.039 --> 00:15:36.559
481.

00:15:37.039 --> 00:15:38.240
480.

00:15:40.120 --> 00:15:41.799
479.

00:15:42.279 --> 00:15:43.360
478.

00:15:43.399 --> 00:15:44.440
Just kill me!

00:15:44.840 --> 00:15:46.120
You foolish mortal!

00:15:46.240 --> 00:15:48.080
I'll kill you!

00:15:52.639 --> 00:15:53.720
Kill me,

00:15:54.120 --> 00:15:55.919
and I'll tell you everything.

00:15:56.120 --> 00:15:57.480
I don't want to know anything.

00:15:58.399 --> 00:15:59.879
What a strange Immortal.

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:04.080
Found it, found it, found it.

00:16:08.480 --> 00:16:11.000
A bit darker than other Immortal Seeds,

00:16:12.080 --> 00:16:13.600
But that's all there is to it.

00:16:15.519 --> 00:16:17.399
Are Immortal Seeds really this weak?

00:16:17.840 --> 00:16:19.759
I just got this body.

00:16:20.360 --> 00:16:22.279
How could I possibly spiritualize it?

00:16:22.360 --> 00:16:23.240
You mean,

00:16:23.639 --> 00:16:24.679
you, as an Immortal,

00:16:24.960 --> 00:16:25.720
are fake?

00:16:30.159 --> 00:16:30.799
Whatever.

00:16:31.679 --> 00:16:33.399
At least it can buy Xiao Baojie

00:16:33.600 --> 00:16:34.679
some more time.

00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:38.759
My work here is done.

00:16:40.159 --> 00:16:41.080
Next up

00:16:41.440 --> 00:16:42.399
is playtime.

00:16:48.240 --> 00:16:49.279
This cut

00:16:50.000 --> 00:16:51.519
is for Houzi.

00:16:52.440 --> 00:16:53.440
This cut

00:16:54.399 --> 00:16:55.879
is also for Houzi.

00:16:56.360 --> 00:16:57.559
This cut

00:16:58.720 --> 00:17:00.600
is also for Houzi.

00:17:01.039 --> 00:17:01.840
This cut

00:17:01.960 --> 00:17:03.320
is for Houzi.

00:17:04.839 --> 00:17:05.720
And this cut

00:17:06.359 --> 00:17:08.319
is still for Houzi.

00:17:13.000 --> 00:17:14.000
If I don't head back soon,

00:17:14.440 --> 00:17:15.759
Xiao Baojie will start to worry.

00:17:26.519 --> 00:17:27.559
You look so pale.

00:17:38.599 --> 00:17:39.400
Good stuff.

00:17:40.039 --> 00:17:40.640
Highly nourishing.

00:17:43.079 --> 00:17:45.039
Only that within three days of taking it,

00:17:45.279 --> 00:17:46.160
you'll die.

00:17:47.039 --> 00:17:48.400
But you don't need to worry.

00:17:48.880 --> 00:17:50.000
You won't live three more days anyway.

00:17:51.160 --> 00:17:51.880
You...

00:17:53.119 --> 00:17:54.400
The gate within you...

00:17:55.359 --> 00:17:56.400
Kill me,

00:17:56.680 --> 00:17:58.440
and I'll tell you how to block it.

00:17:59.160 --> 00:17:59.799
Otherwise,

00:18:00.359 --> 00:18:02.920
revived Immortals will still kill you.

00:18:03.319 --> 00:18:04.599
Why would I want to block them?

00:18:04.920 --> 00:18:06.000
If I block them,

00:18:06.119 --> 00:18:07.119
how will they find me?

00:18:07.559 --> 00:18:09.000
If they can't find me,

00:18:09.400 --> 00:18:11.160
how to get Xiao Baojie an Immortal Seed?

00:18:23.000 --> 00:18:23.599
Now,

00:18:34.480 --> 00:18:35.359
get some rest.

00:18:35.920 --> 00:18:37.000
I'll drop by again when I have time.